      <title>Hexo &amp; 腾讯云  &amp; GitHub 搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2022/07/31/Hello%20Word/"/>
      <url>/2022/07/31/Hello%20Word/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="Hexo-amp-腾讯云-amp-GitHub-搭建个人博客"><a href="#Hexo-amp-腾讯云-amp-GitHub-搭建个人博客" class="headerlink" title="Hexo &amp; 腾讯云  &amp; GitHub 搭建个人博客"></a>Hexo &amp; 腾讯云  &amp; GitHub 搭建个人博客</h1><div class="note info modern"><p>注意：在此之前，假设你已经知道了怎么配置服务器和域名</p></div><p><img src="https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/08/01/F7GJg.png" alt="博客页面"></p><div class="note info modern"><p><strong>该博文大致分为三块：</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>本地部署</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>GitHub部署</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>服务器部署</strong></p><p>……</p></li></ul></div><h2 id="本地部署"><a href="#本地部署" class="headerlink" title="本地部署"></a>本地部署</h2><hr><h3 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h3><hr><p>系统：Windows10 </p><p>安装：</p><ul><li><p><strong><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">Node.js</a></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><a href="https://git-scm.com/">git</a></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">Hexo</a></strong></p></li></ul><blockquote><p>假设上述都以安装完毕</p></blockquote><p>开始本地部署：</p><ol><li><p>首先需要在电脑上新建一个博客文件夹，作为博客的根目录，列如<mark class="hl-label pink">~D:/Hexo/</mark> ,为了在此文章中方便的诠释，所以使用[BlogRoot] 指代博客的根目录</p></li><li><p>在 [BlogRoot] 路径右键 -&gt; Git Bash Here, 输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config set registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br><span class="line">#将npm源替换为阿里的镜像。之后的安装就会迅速很多了。</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line"># hexo-cli 是 hexo的指令集。</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>初始化 Hexo 博客</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">## 本地创建一个目录用于存放博客</span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在浏览器中打开 <a href="localhost:4000">localhost:4000</a>,就能看到自己的博客页面了</p><blockquote><p>注意看</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/08/01/FHmZN.png" alt="Fe8Yn.png"></p></li></ol><div class="note info modern"><p>恭喜你，本地部署完成 ！</p></div><h2 id="GitHub部署"><a href="#GitHub部署" class="headerlink" title="GitHub部署"></a>GitHub部署</h2><hr><p><strong>注册 github</strong></p><hr><p><a href="https://github.com/">注册github</a>,用户名记着下面需要用</p><br><p><strong>新建仓库</strong></p><hr><p>新建 username.github.io 仓库:</p><p>注册成功后，在 github 首页单机头像 -&gt; Your repositories 在自己的 GitHub 账号下创建y一个新的仓库, 命名为 username.github.io</p><blockquote><p>username 是你的用户名</p></blockquote><br><p><strong>配置 Git 与 GitHub:</strong></p><hr><p>此处为全局配置，可以在任意位置打开 git bash , 设置用户名称和邮箱地址</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;haiyong&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;1836360247@qq.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>本地获取公钥</strong></p><hr><blockquote><p>假设是第一次使用 git 本机不存在公钥的情况下，需要生成公钥，如果已经存在公钥，直接跳过这一步</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;xxxxx@xxxxx.com&quot;  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>按照提示完成三次回车，即可生成 ssh key</p><p>看看本机的公钥：</p><ul><li>Windows 10 : C:&#x2F;Users&#x2F;ASUS&#x2F;.ssh</li></ul><p>以我的电脑举例：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cat C:/Users/lenovo/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将结果复制保存</p><br><p><strong>将 SSH Keys 保存到 GitHub</strong> </p><hr><p>打开 github 点击头像 -&gt;settings, 在设置页面找到 SSH and GPG keys，单击 New SSH key 新建 SSH KEY。</p><p><img src="https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/08/01/FHjpd.png"></p><br><p><strong>测试 ssh key 是否添加成功</strong></p><hr><p>在 git bash 测试 sshkey 是否添加成功，输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第一次链接测试需要输入yes，正常输出是：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">The authenticity of host &#x27;github.com (207.97.227.239)&#x27; can&#x27;t be established.</span><br><span class="line">RSA key fingerprint is 16:27:ac:a5:76:28:2d:36:63:1b:56:4d:eb:df:a6:48.</span><br><span class="line">Are you sure you want to continue connecting (yes/no)?</span><br><span class="line"># 此处请输入yes</span><br><span class="line">Hi username! You&#x27;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not</span><br><span class="line">provide shell access.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>配置 Hexo 部署插件</strong></p><hr><p>确保你是否安装了 hexo-deployer-git , 如果没有，在 [BlogRoot] 路径右键 -&gt; Git Bash Here, 输入：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>修改 deploy 配置项</strong></p><hr><p>打开 [BlogRoot]&#x2F;_config.yml, 修改底部的 deploy 配置项</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repository:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:cndadi/cndadi.github.io.git</span>  <span class="comment">#你的仓库地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note info modern"><p>到这里假设以上内容已经全部配置完毕，现在只需要把本地 hexo 博客内容提交到 git 仓库，就能实现在 github 上部署个人博客</p></div><br><p><strong>部署</strong></p><hr><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在可以在浏览器上输入 username.gtihub.io 访问你的博客了</p><blockquote><p>username.github 用户名</p></blockquote><br><h2 id="腾讯云部署"><a href="#腾讯云部署" class="headerlink" title="腾讯云部署"></a>腾讯云部署</h2><hr><p>有了上述部署到 github 的经验，现在将 Hexo 部署到 腾讯云上</p><div class="note info modern"><p>本文略过 购买服务器 ，配置服务器 的过程，假设你已经配置完成了</p></div><p>接下来的步骤大致如下：</p><ul><li>服务器安装 Nodejs</li><li>服务器安装 git</li><li>服务器安装 Nginx</li><li>客户端安装 Hexo</li><li>客户端配置免密登录</li><li>服务器创建 git 仓库</li><li>Hexo 主题配置</li></ul><br><p><strong>服务器安装 Nodejs</strong></p><hr><p>在本地客户端使用 ssh 链接腾讯云服务器公网 ip ：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh root@公网Ip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>一键安装配置 Nodejs ：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /tmp &amp;&amp; wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v17.5.0/node-v17.5.0-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br><span class="line">tar xf node-v17.5.0-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br><span class="line">mv node-v17.5.0-linux-x64 /usr/local/node</span><br><span class="line">ln -s /usr/local/node/bin/node /bin/node</span><br><span class="line">ln -s /usr/local/node/bin/npm /bin/npm</span><br><span class="line">echo &#x27;export PATH=/usr/local/node/bin:$PATH&#x27; &gt;&gt; /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line">source /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行完就安装成功了</p><br><p><strong>服务器安装 Git</strong></p><hr><p>一键安装 Git:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y curl-devel expat-devel gettext-devel openssl-devel zlib-devel gcc perl-ExtUtils-MakeMaker</span><br><span class="line">cd /tmp &amp;&amp; wget https://www.kernel.org/pub/software/scm/git/git-2.9.5.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">tar xf git-2.9.5.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">cd git-2.9.5 &amp;&amp; make all prefix=/usr/local/git</span><br><span class="line">make install prefix=/usr/local/git</span><br><span class="line">echo &#x27;export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/git/bin&#x27; &gt;&gt; /etc/bashrc</span><br><span class="line">source /etc/bashrc</span><br><span class="line">git version</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;你的账号&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行完就安装成功了，要注意的是本地也需要安装一下 Git，图形化一直下一步就行。</p><p><strong>服务器安装 Nginx</strong> </p><hr><p>一键安装 Nginx:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y gcc gcc-c++ pcre pcre-devel zlib zlib-devel openssl openssl-devel</span><br><span class="line">cd /tmp &amp;&amp; wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.9.9.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">tar xf nginx-1.9.9.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">cd nginx-1.9.9 &amp;&amp; ./configure</span><br><span class="line">make &amp;&amp; make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>配置 Nginx 服务:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">## 创建 hexo 博客存放位置</span><br><span class="line">mkdir /data/blog</span><br><span class="line">## 修改 Nginx 配置文件</span><br><span class="line">vi /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">## 修改配置文件中以下几点</span><br><span class="line">## 1、server_name，修改域名或ip</span><br><span class="line">server_name  服务器公网IP;</span><br><span class="line">## 2、root index.html，修改为 hexo 博客存放的位置</span><br><span class="line">root /data/blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开 Nginx 服务:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /usr/local/nginx/sbin</span><br><span class="line"># 启动 nginx</span><br><span class="line">./nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到这里 Nginx 就已经安装并且启动了</p><br><p><strong>客户端安装 Hexo</strong></p><hr><div class="note info modern"><p>还记得吗，我们在第一步的时候就已经创建好我们的本地博客了，所以这里就略过，不会的话请回到 <mark class="hl-label default">本地部署</mark>  中查看</p></div><br><p><strong>配置免密登录</strong></p><hr><p>配置本地和服务器的 ssh 免密登录，方便一键上传</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">## 执行完之后一直回车就行</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen</span><br><span class="line">## 上传公共密钥到阿里云服务器</span><br><span class="line">ssh-copy-id root@阿里云公网IP</span><br><span class="line">## 测试是否已免密</span><br><span class="line">ssh root@阿里云公网IP</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果无需密码即可登录，说明已经配置完成</p><br><p><strong>服务器创建 Git 仓库</strong></p><hr><p>服务器上创建一个 Git 仓库，该仓库中新建一个 post-receive 钩子文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ~</span><br><span class="line">git init --bare hexo.git</span><br><span class="line">vi ~/hexo.git/hooks/post-receive</span><br><span class="line">## 填写以下内容，其中的--work-tree 为 hexo 博客目录</span><br><span class="line">git --work-tree=/data/blog --git-dir=/root/hexo.git checkout -f</span><br><span class="line">## 授予钩子文件可执行权限</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x ~/hexo.git/hooks/post-receive</span><br><span class="line">chmod -R 777 /data/blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到此，Git 仓库创建并且配置完成了。</p><p>现在只需要配置我们本地的配置，然后部署到服务器上就完成了</p><p>在 [HexoRoot] 中，找到 _config.yml ，在文本末尾的 deploy ，对其进行参数修改：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Deployment</span><br><span class="line">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: root@公网IP:/root/hexo.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在本地计算机安装插件 :   hexo-deployer-git 和 hexo-server , 插件的作用分别是使用 Git 自动部署，和 hexo 本地简单的服务器：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-server</span><br><span class="line">## 配置全局变量</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;你的账号&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span><br><span class="line">## 生成发布 Hexo 博客</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到这里，便可以通过浏览器访问： <a href="http://aixuxu.ltd/">http:&#x2F;&#x2F;腾讯云公网Ip</a> 进入 hexo 的博客主页了</p><blockquote><p>通过以上三种方式部署 Hexo 博客之后，就拥有了一个简单的个人博客网站，但是怎么修改网站的一些初始化信息呢？</p></blockquote><h2 id="Hexo-基础修改"><a href="#Hexo-基础修改" class="headerlink" title="Hexo 基础修改"></a>Hexo 基础修改</h2><hr><div class="note info modern"><p>在基础修改之前，得明白 [HexoRoot] 目录下得 _config.yml 是 Hexo 的主配置文件， _config.主题.yml 是 主题的配置文件，那么这两个文件有什么区别呢？</p><ul><li><code>_config.yml </code>：配置自己的基本信息，比如使用哪个 hexo 主题，网站标题写什么，副标题写什么，网站名写什么等等</li><li><code>_config</code>.主题.yml: 配置主题的参数信息，比如配置网站的背景，网站的一些组件，网站的整体调色等等</li></ul></div><p><strong>修改博客主题</strong></p><hr><p>这里选择的是  Butterfly 主题</p><p>在 [BlogRoot] 目录中鼠标右击 -&gt; Git-Bush-Here ：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 等待克隆完成，在 [BlogRoot] 目录的 themes 文件下会看到   <strong>butterfly</strong>文件夹，将该文件夹中的 <code>_config.yml</code> 的文件内容拷贝到 [BlogRoot] 文件夹下的 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 中，</p><blockquote><p>[BlogRoot] 目录下没有 _config.butterfly.yml 的话，新建一个就好了，再将主题目录 themes -&gt; butterfly 中的 _config.yml 的内容拷贝到 _config.butterfly.yml 中即可，这样做是为了以后更新主题时防止覆盖之前的主题配置</p></blockquote><p>接下来在 [BlogRoot] 目录 的 _config.yml 中修改配置信息：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Extensions</span><br><span class="line">## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</span><br><span class="line">## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</span><br><span class="line">theme: butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新启动本地 hexo 服务</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>修改网站资料</strong></p><hr><p>修改网站各种资料，例如标题、副标题和邮箱等个人资料，请修改博客根目录的站点配置文件 _config.yml：</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Ai</span> <span class="string">Xu</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;(｡･∀･)ﾉﾞ嗨&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;乐于记录笔记与过往&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">Ai</span> <span class="string">Xu</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>导航菜单</strong></p><hr><p>修改 [BlogRoot] 目录的 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code>文件：</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="string">首页:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="string">目录||fas</span> <span class="attr">fa-list:</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">归档:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">分类:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-folder-open</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">#音乐: /music/ || fas fa-music</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">#Movie: /movies/ || fas fa-video</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="string">传送门:</span> <span class="string">/link/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-link</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="comment">#关于: /about/ || fas fa-heart</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><h3 id="博客关键页面生成"><a href="#博客关键页面生成" class="headerlink" title="博客关键页面生成"></a><strong>博客关键页面生成</strong></h3><hr><p>博客有一些关键页面需要手动生成。</p><br><p><strong>标签页</strong></p><hr><p>在 [BlogRoot] 目录中，鼠标右击 -&gt; Git-Bush-Here 执行:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开 <code>source/tags/index.md</code> 文件，修改如下：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 标签</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-03-11 12:53:45</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>分类页</strong></p><hr><p>在 [BlogRoot] 目录中，鼠标右击 -&gt; Git-Bush-Here 执行:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开 <code>source/categories/index.md</code> 文件，修改如下：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-03-11 12:56:06</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>友链页</strong></p><hr><p><strong>创建友链页面</strong></p><p>在 [BlogRoot] 目录中，鼠标右击 -&gt; Git-Bush-Here 执行:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page link</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开 <code>source/link/index.md</code> 文件，修改如下：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 友情链接</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-03-11 12:57:48</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">type: &quot;link&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>友链添加</strong></p><p>在 [BlogRoot] 目录中 <code> source/_data</code>（如果没有该文件，请自行创建），创建一个文件 <code>link.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">class_name:</span> <span class="string">本站</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">class_desc:</span> <span class="string">交换友链可在下方评论，或者微信/QQ联系我</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">link_list:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Ai</span> <span class="string">xu</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">link:</span> <span class="string">https://aixuxu.ltd</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">https://aixuxu.ltd/img/favicon.png</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">descr:</span> <span class="string">一个用于记录笔记和过往的小博客</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">class_name:</span> <span class="string">网站</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">class_desc:</span> <span class="string">值得推荐的网站</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">link_list:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Youtube</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">link:</span> <span class="string">https://www.youtube.com/</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">https://i.loli.net/2020/05/14/9ZkGg8v3azHJfM1.png</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">descr:</span> <span class="string">视频网站</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Weibo</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">link:</span> <span class="string">https://www.weibo.com/</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">https://i.loli.net/2020/05/14/TLJBum386vcnI1P.png</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">descr:</span> <span class="string">中国最大社交分享平台</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Twitter</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">link:</span> <span class="string">https://twitter.com/</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">https://i.loli.net/2020/05/14/5VyHPQqR6LWF39a.png</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">descr:</span> <span class="string">社交分享平台</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><p><strong>关于我</strong></p><hr><p>在 [BlogRoot] 目录中，鼠标右击 -&gt; Git-Bush-Here 执行:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page about</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开 <code>source/abount/index.md</code>文件，修改：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 关于我</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-07-31 17:43:48</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;about&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note info modern"><p>至此，简单的 Hexo 博客框架就完成搭建了，至于更多的美化可以参考 ：<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/4aa8abbe/">Butterfly 安装文档</a></p></div><p>可以说是完全参考了该文章：<a href="https://juejin.cn/post/7121277225390833700#heading-27">Hexo+阿里云&amp;GitHub 搭建个人博客 - 掘金 (juejin.cn)</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
